flowchart TD
  A([Claim received with sensor bundle]) --> B

  B["Check movement continuity\n(accelerometer + GPS breadcrumbs)"]
  B --> C{Physically plausible?}
  C -->|Yes| D[Movement score: LOW]
  C -->|No| E["Movement score: HIGH\n(impossible speed or jump)"]

  D & E --> F["Check device integrity\n(mock location, root, emulator flags)"]
  F --> G{Attestation passes?}
  G -->|Yes| H[Device score: LOW]
  G -->|No| I[Device score: HIGH]

  H & I --> J["Fetch hyperlocal weather\n+ nearby disruption data"]
  J --> K{Environment matches\nclaimed disruption?}
  K -->|Yes| L[Environment: CORROBORATED]
  K -->|No| M[Environment: INCONSISTENT]

  L & M --> N[Load worker historical reliability score]

  N --> O["Compute Individual Risk Score (0-10)\n--------------------------\nMovement continuity  30%\nDevice integrity     25%\nEnvironmental match  20%\nHistorical reliability 15%\nBehavioral anomaly   10%"]

  O --> P["Run cluster check\n(recent claims, same geo-cell,\nlast 15 min, radius < 2km)"]
  P --> Q{"5+ claims with shared\nfingerprints or sync timestamps?"}
  Q -->|Yes| R["Elevate cluster risk score\nTrigger geo-cell circuit breaker"]
  Q -->|No| S[Cluster score: NORMAL]

  R & S --> T([Route to Decision Engine])
